    "'{tag}' is too common to guess. Try a more specific tag!": "'{tag}' 太常見了，無法猜測。請嘗試更具體的標籤！",
    "(Note: Gelbooru & Danbooru totals are only accurate with an API key. Other counts are scraped.)": "(注意：Gelbooru 和 Danbooru 的總數只有在使用 API 金鑰時才準確。其他計數是抓取而來的。)",
