    "<h2>Send a message to begin a conversation!</h2>": "<h2>Send a message to begin a conversation!</h2>",
    "<h2>Welcome to Snekbooru!</h2><p>Please set up the essentials. You can change all of these and more in the main settings later.</p>": "<h2>歡迎使用 Snekbooru！</h2><p>請先完成基本設定。您稍後可以在主設定中變更所有這些項目以及更多設定。</p>",
    "<h3>Guess the Missing Tag</h3>One tag has been hidden. Can you guess what it is?": "<h3>猜猜看缺少的標籤</h3>其中一個標籤被隱藏了。您能猜到是什麼嗎？",
    "<h3>Guess the Score</h3>Guess the exact score of the image!": "<h3>猜猜看分數</h3>猜猜看圖片的確切分數！",
    "<h3>Score Showdown</h3>Which post has the higher score? Choose one!": "<h3>分數對決</h3>哪一篇貼文的分數比較高？選一個！",
    "<h3>Tag Guesser</h3>Guess one of the tags for the image shown!": "<h3>標籤猜謎</h3>猜猜看顯示圖片的其中一個標籤！",
    "<i>...and a big thanks to all the users there!</i>": "<i>...以及非常感謝那裡的所有使用者！</i>",
